Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 4: A Hero Must Seek No Reward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a special key to get through the\Ncaves that lead to the Kingdom of Geldovar!\NEpisode 4: A Hero Must Seek No Reward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a special key to get through the\Ncaves that lead to the Kingdom of Geldovar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And only I have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want it, you have to do what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quite rude, isn't he?  Shall I kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what he'll make us do,\Nbut I'm sure it's a trial fit for a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is it okay to have Fighter-san\Ndo this all by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she'd do it.  Why not let her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Carrying things isn't a job fit for a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.43,0:00:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Catch a dog that ran away"?\NIs this also a hero's job?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop!  That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop! I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is supposedly a new medicine\Ndeveloped by the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants me to drink it and see what it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good can come of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a hero's job!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No!  If I don't drink it, we cannot progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also a hero's job!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My body feels so warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so suddenly?\NIt's still the middle of the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You like that?  You like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,People are watching.\NYou like that?  You like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that somewhere else.\NYou like that?  You like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't do it anywhere else, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I defeat this monster\Nlike the mayor said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll finally get that key...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lose! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No!  No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't get on with it,\Nour adventure will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable!  Having all\Nthat fun by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No... it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.  Let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!  You have completed all my tasks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are true heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... then like you promised,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll give us the key we absolutely need\Nto get to the Kingdom of Geldovar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... the key is already within you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,By obeying my unreasonable commands,\Nyou learned the importance of helping others!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That experience is the key that every\Nadventurer absolutely requires!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You are true heroes!  I'm so moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.  Don't stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just don't kill him...